snippet.textDisplay:
My sincere appeal to all the listeners ! Please listen the original one with less music and more voice. You will flow with the mesmerizing flavour of this very original song.
You know, till today, RANGABATI, still stands 1st in the line of most famous hit songs of Odisha. The credit belongs to Krishna Patel, Jitendriya Haripal, Mitrabhanu Gauntia and Prabhudutta Pradhan.
snippet.textOriginal:

snippet.textDisplay:
What is magical about their voices? They might have good voices but that does not enable them to kill the very ambience of these two most popular and historical songs in the history of Odisha. I really can't catch the idea of putting a South Indian dialogue rendition there.
I am not disrespecting any language or artist. However, these adaptations and their presentations are neither melodious nor soulful.
